    "description": "<p>BUREAU VERITAS SINGAPORE PTE. LTD.</p>    <p>Bureau Veritas is an international group with a core business of conformity assessment, applied in the areas of quality, health, safety, environment and social accountability. Founded in 1828, Bureau Veritas currently has over 64,000 employees globally spread across 1,330 offices in 140 countries. Bureau Veritas is listed in the Paris Stock Exchange and is recognized and accredited by large national and international bodies. Today, Bureau Veritas serves more than 400,000 customers throughout the world.</p>  ",
